\backslash
ref{tab:redist}
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 We calculate effects measured both as a percentage of each consumer group's baseline expenditures as well as in terms of overall dollars when the total expenditures across all consumers are scaled up to around 
\begin_inset Formula $\$12$
\end_inset

 trillion.
 On average,
 cash-using consumers would be better off by 
